signing of an agreement granting independence to southwest africa 
better known as namibia it was signed thursday by south africa 
angola and cuba which agreed to withdraw its 50000 troops from 
angola 
the assembly will reconvene in midjanuary to discuss financial 
questions and funding of a un monitoring force in southwest 
africa 
