about a threat made against pan am flights because the information 
was considered confidential an official said friday 
the department of transport said british airports also were not 
told about the information passed on by us authorities the threat 
mentioned a pan am flight from frankfurt west germany and did not 
specifically mention britain 
transport minister michael portillo said in a british 
